satellite.heading: Setilayiti
satellite.specs:
Ebipimo: mm 50x58x64
1P EnsawoQube
Obuzito: 245 gr
Ebikozesebwa: aluminiyamu, zaabu, fiberglass, n’ebitundu by’ebyuma.
Enkulungo: Obugulumivu bwa kiromita 525 ± 25; okuserengeta: SSO 97.6 ± 0.1°
Ekyuma ekisimbula: PSLV (Polar Satellite Launch Vehicle) eddukanyizibwa kkampuni ya ISRO

antenna.heading: Antenna/Ekibumbe
antenna.specs:
Ebipimo: 6 m (obuwanvu) e 1.2m (obugulumivu)
Obuzito: Kkiro 46
Ebikozesebwa: aluminiyamu, epoxy mirrored board, zaabu aluminiyamu dome ewaniriddwa okuyita mu kizimbe kya scaffolding.

radio.heading: Ebikwata ku leediyo
radio.specs:
Enkola y’okukka wansi: 468.5 MHz
Okukyusakyusa: CSS
